1602
00:42:58,800 --> 00:42:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] i onda stalno otiskamo

1603
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] nova izdanja,

1604
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] sad će ići peto,

1605
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] iće posebno zlatno izdanje,

1606
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] tvrde korice,

1607
00:43:04,119 --> 00:43:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] ono.

1608
00:43:04,699 --> 00:43:06,400
[SPEAKER_02] Super, ajde, čestitam,

1609
00:43:06,400 --> 00:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] drago mi je.

1610
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,400
[SPEAKER_02] Religiozno si kažeš,

1611
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,940
[SPEAKER_02] Boga si unio ju

1612
00:43:11,940 --> 00:43:13,639
[SPEAKER_02] u svoj psihoterapijski

1613
00:43:13,639 --> 00:43:15,320
[SPEAKER_02] slaš knjuževni rad,

1614
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:17,000
[SPEAKER_02] a svakako je dio tvoga,

1615
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,139
[SPEAKER_02] svakodnevnog života.

1616
00:43:18,139 --> 00:43:19,639
[SPEAKER_02] Jutro ste obilozili crkve

1617
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:20,900
[SPEAKER_02] po Mostaru, je li tako?

1618
00:43:20,980 --> 00:43:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] Pa jesmo, da.

1619
00:43:21,559 --> 00:43:24,539
[SPEAKER_02] Što još znači živjeti vjeru danas?

1620
00:43:24,539 --> 00:43:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja bih rekao da

1621
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] danas je teško biti vjernik,

1622
00:43:30,420 --> 00:43:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] ono, vjernik u smislu

1623
00:43:32,039 --> 00:43:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] autentičnog vjernika

1624
00:43:33,019 --> 00:43:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji živi svakodnevni,

1625
00:43:34,719 --> 00:43:35,280
[SPEAKER_00] ono, zbogom,

1626
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] bez neke zajednice.

1627
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] Smatram da živjeti s braćom u zajednici

1628
00:43:38,860 --> 00:43:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] je meni pomoglo da vidiš

1629
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo ko si ti,

1630
00:43:41,760 --> 00:43:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] kakav jesi,

1631
00:43:42,579 --> 00:43:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer su braća često iskrena prema tebi

1632
00:43:44,420 --> 00:43:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] i kroz taj hod,

1633
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] hod kroz zajednicu

1634
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] i prolaske razno raznih tema

1635
00:43:50,980 --> 00:43:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] i drugih događaja u zajednici

1636
00:43:53,519 --> 00:43:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] osoba produbljuje svoj odnos s Bogom.

1637
00:43:55,179 --> 00:43:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da to kao ja kao osoba

1638
00:43:56,599 --> 00:43:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi nikad sam uspio.

1639
00:43:57,960 --> 00:43:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Neko možda hoće.

1640
00:43:58,980 --> 00:44:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne kažem da zajednica koja ja jesam

1641
00:44:01,599 --> 00:44:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] je najbolje najispravnija.

1642
00:44:02,599 --> 00:44:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1643
00:44:02,780 --> 00:44:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Ivan Pavel II.

1644
00:44:04,139 --> 00:44:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] kad je usvajao naše statute

1645
00:44:06,139 --> 00:44:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] je rekao da je to

1646
00:44:06,900 --> 00:44:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] ispravan put krećanske inicijacije u vjeru.

1647
00:44:09,280 --> 00:44:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan od ispravnih putova.

1648
00:44:12,139 --> 00:44:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja sam se pronašao u tome

1649
00:44:13,679 --> 00:44:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] i vidim da mi to pomaže.

1650
00:44:14,679 --> 00:44:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam bio u nekim životnim

1651
00:44:16,019 --> 00:44:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] najvećim tim krizama i dubiozama,

1652
00:44:18,599 --> 00:44:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] psihologija mi je bila okej,

1653
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi je zajednica najviše pomogla.

1654
00:44:22,579 --> 00:44:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] To da sam bio iskreno u zajednici

1655
00:44:23,800 --> 00:44:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] i iskreno pričao o problemima

1656
00:44:26,079 --> 00:44:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi se događaju.

1657
00:44:26,920 --> 00:44:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Onda meni često ljudi kažu

1658
00:44:28,340 --> 00:44:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] da njema zajednica zvuči

1659
00:44:29,699 --> 00:44:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] kao grupna terapija.

1660
00:44:30,639 --> 00:44:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što donekle i je.

1661
00:44:32,559 --> 00:44:33,719
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo.

1662
00:44:33,719 --> 00:44:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se mi kao braća u zajednici nađemo

1663
00:44:35,519 --> 00:44:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] neka je tema,

1664
00:44:36,539 --> 00:44:38,360
[SPEAKER_00] ti daješ neko svoje iskustvo.

1665
00:44:38,360 --> 00:44:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] Osobno način nije da ti drugima

1666
00:44:40,559 --> 00:44:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] nešto pametuješ.

1667
00:44:41,239 --> 00:44:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet to je tako kao

1668
00:44:42,719 --> 00:44:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] u grupnoj terapiji

1669
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti govoriš iz ja,

1670
00:44:45,519 --> 00:44:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] ono ovdje i sada

1671
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] i mi nemamo voditelja

1672
00:44:49,500 --> 00:44:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji bude svećenik s nama,

1673
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

1674
00:44:50,900 --> 00:44:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] subotom ne koristi i tako dalje.

1675
00:44:52,920 --> 00:44:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] I onda,

1676
00:44:53,199 --> 00:44:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali kažem opet ti

1677
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] ti razvijaš svoj odnos sa Bogom

1678
00:44:57,559 --> 00:44:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] hodajući u zajednici.

1679
00:44:59,219 --> 00:45:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja, kažem,

1680
00:45:00,099 --> 00:45:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] meni ona neprocijenjivo blago

1681
00:45:01,420 --> 00:45:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne bi sigurno bio ovako hrabar

1682
00:45:05,099 --> 00:45:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] i imao više djece.

1683
00:45:06,139 --> 00:45:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] Možda se ne bi ni ženio.

1684
00:45:07,179 --> 00:45:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam u zajednici,

1685
00:45:08,579 --> 00:45:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam vidio te ljude

1686
00:45:09,340 --> 00:45:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju više djece,

1687
00:45:10,119 --> 00:45:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] da se može živjeti s više djece,

1688
00:45:11,599 --> 00:45:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog proviđa.

1689
00:45:12,380 --> 00:45:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] I mislim da danas ljudima

1690
00:45:13,960 --> 00:45:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] fali po meni

1691
00:45:15,800 --> 00:45:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] to da vjeru da Bog proviđa.

1692
00:45:17,460 --> 00:45:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da bi puno više ljudi

1693
00:45:19,039 --> 00:45:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] imalo više djece

1694
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi znali da,

1695
00:45:21,780 --> 00:45:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je ono skoku vjeri

1696
00:45:23,360 --> 00:45:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] da ti prvo ti imaš šestero djece,

1697
00:45:25,619 --> 00:45:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] a onda Bog pošalje minibus.

1698
00:45:27,099 --> 00:45:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] Niko neće kupiti minibus

1699
00:45:29,139 --> 00:45:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednim djetetom.

1700
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:30,940
[SPEAKER_02] A što znači još

1701
00:45:30,940 --> 00:45:32,179
[SPEAKER_02] sljedočiti vjeru danas?

1702
00:45:32,179 --> 00:45:32,860
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim ti si,

1703
00:45:32,860 --> 00:45:35,019
[SPEAKER_02] ne li biš se reći o svoje stavove?

1704
00:45:35,019 --> 00:45:35,619
[SPEAKER_02] Pa gledaj,

1705
00:45:35,619 --> 00:45:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad imaš šestero djece,

1706
00:45:36,539 --> 00:45:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] nemenovno ja,

1707
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] čim hodaš po ulici,

1708
00:45:38,960 --> 00:45:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] već si neki znak.

1709
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] A ja često sebe gledam,

1710
00:45:40,820 --> 00:45:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] da li bi mogli džana ja više,

1711
00:45:41,960 --> 00:45:42,679
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mogo bolje,

1712
00:45:42,679 --> 00:45:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] da li bi mogo ja nešto.

1713
00:45:43,579 --> 00:45:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ponekad kad se forsiraš,

1714
00:45:45,960 --> 00:45:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] ispadne bez veze,

1715
00:45:46,699 --> 00:45:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] ispadne nejako naporno.

1716
00:45:47,840 --> 00:45:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ovako kad imaš više djece

1717
00:45:50,260 --> 00:45:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] i ljudi ti često priđu

1718
00:45:52,139 --> 00:45:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] dakle na snaga i harabrost

1719
00:45:53,139 --> 00:45:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] i onda mati ti si psiholog

1720
00:45:55,099 --> 00:45:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] i onda tu si uvijek u napasti

1721
00:45:56,380 --> 00:45:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] i znaš,

1722
00:45:56,760 --> 00:45:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] stavite psihologiju na prvo mjesto,

1723
00:45:58,639 --> 00:45:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda je kažem,

1724
00:45:59,260 --> 00:46:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] gledaj, da nema Boga,

1725
00:46:00,059 --> 00:46:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja sigurno ne bi imao toliko djece.

1726
00:46:01,320 --> 00:46:02,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jer bilo bi teško,

1727
00:46:02,739 --> 00:46:03,480
[SPEAKER_00] ljudski glavno je teško

1728
00:46:03,480 --> 00:46:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] i što ti ti kažu,

1729
00:46:04,539 --> 00:46:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] odi u parku kad se jedno s nama na kavu,

1730
00:46:05,920 --> 00:46:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] ono pa kako,

1731
00:46:06,940 --> 00:46:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] pa taman je ovo zadnje sad,

1732
00:46:08,159 --> 00:46:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] imamo dvije godine tima djete,

1733
00:46:09,619 --> 00:46:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] naučilo je spavat cijelu noć,

1734
00:46:11,559 --> 00:46:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] više se ne budi,

1735
00:46:12,440 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] zna pričat, jede samo,

1736
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] nema više pelene

1737
00:46:14,940 --> 00:46:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] i sad opet ideš u sve.

1738
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:17,539
[SPEAKER_02] Da, mislim, to skroz ima smisla

1739
00:46:17,539 --> 00:46:19,320
[SPEAKER_02] jer ti daje hrabrost

1740
00:46:19,320 --> 00:46:21,579
[SPEAKER_02] za koju smatraš da je nemaš,

1741
00:46:21,579 --> 00:46:22,699
[SPEAKER_02] da nemaš kapacitete.

1742
00:46:22,699 --> 00:46:23,079
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, recimo,

1743
00:46:23,079 --> 00:46:27,039
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću to iz osobne neke pozicije reći

1744
00:46:27,039 --> 00:46:29,219
[SPEAKER_02] da u toj nekoj potrošenosti

1745
00:46:32,739 --> 00:46:34,440
[SPEAKER_02] i sad neke stvari

1746
00:46:34,440 --> 00:46:36,119
[SPEAKER_02] koje kod sebe primjećuje manjkeve,

1747
00:46:36,119 --> 00:46:36,780
[SPEAKER_02] zapitam se,

1748
00:46:36,780 --> 00:46:37,579
[SPEAKER_02] pa šta bi još,

1749
00:46:37,579 --> 00:46:38,500
[SPEAKER_02] da imam još bebu,

1750
00:46:38,500 --> 00:46:39,659
[SPEAKER_02] kako bi ja to,

1751
00:46:39,659 --> 00:46:41,440
[SPEAKER_02] bili imala kapacitet za to?

1752
00:46:41,440 --> 00:46:43,480
[SPEAKER_02] Kako vi jačate kapacitete?

1753
00:46:43,480 --> 00:46:44,460
[SPEAKER_02] Je li kroz molitvu?

1754
00:46:44,460 --> 00:46:45,719
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ja bih rekao da mi zajednica

1755
00:46:45,719 --> 00:46:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] mi daje jako puno snage,

1756
00:46:46,860 --> 00:46:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] evo, molitva i zajednica.

1757
00:46:48,320 --> 00:46:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, i okej,

1758
00:46:49,940 --> 00:46:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sad baš ovaj,

1759
00:46:50,900 --> 00:46:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] ovi stariji kad vide da je situacija panike,

1760
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] onda oni su dobro,

1761
00:46:54,780 --> 00:46:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, moću reći,

1762
00:46:55,420 --> 00:46:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] oni su dobro, dobri su,

1763
00:46:56,599 --> 00:46:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] znaš, ono, odrade svoj dio

1764
00:46:57,619 --> 00:46:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji trebaju pomažu po kući,

1765
00:46:59,440 --> 00:47:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] to smo već rekli,

1766
00:47:00,260 --> 00:47:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] pranje zubiju,

1767
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] stari sami,

1768
00:47:02,719 --> 00:47:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] onda ja ovima,

1769
00:47:03,340 --> 00:47:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] mlađa malo,

1770
00:47:04,659 --> 00:47:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] kažem je zubar,

1771
00:47:05,420 --> 00:47:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] onda do desete godine

1772
00:47:06,300 --> 00:47:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] moraš ti za djecom popravljati,

1773
00:47:08,280 --> 00:47:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] jer fina motorika se,

1774
00:47:10,260 --> 00:47:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] ta za baš za pranje zubiju,

1775
00:47:11,380 --> 00:47:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] se kaže žena usvaja s deset godina,

1776
00:47:12,780 --> 00:47:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] to je zubarski recept,

1777
00:47:14,400 --> 00:47:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] to nije psihologija,

1778
00:47:15,159 --> 00:47:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali kažem,

1779
00:47:16,119 --> 00:47:17,739
[SPEAKER_02] evo, ja popratim,

1780
00:47:17,739 --> 00:47:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

1781
00:47:18,139 --> 00:47:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] to su već strani zubi,

1782
00:47:19,380 --> 00:47:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

1783
00:47:19,519 --> 00:47:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] Na veče ponekad ja čitam priču,

1784
00:47:22,519 --> 00:47:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] ponekad puštamo sa YouTube-a priče,

1785
00:47:24,639 --> 00:47:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] pustim često neku muziku za spavanje,

1786
00:47:27,099 --> 00:47:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] ono što meni kažu ljudi.

1787
00:47:29,039 --> 00:47:30,719
[SPEAKER_02] Što kako to ide sa uspavljivanjem,

1788
00:47:30,719 --> 00:47:32,639
[SPEAKER_02] to je u ostalom bilo jedno od pitanja?

1789
00:47:32,639 --> 00:47:33,679
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, gle,

1790
00:47:33,679 --> 00:47:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono što ja vidim i u vrtuću,

1791
00:47:35,000 --> 00:47:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] što me ljudi pitaju,

1792
00:47:35,719 --> 00:47:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] kako mi to rješavamo,

1793
00:47:36,599 --> 00:47:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ja djecu ne uspavljujem,

1794
00:47:37,920 --> 00:47:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] mi se s njima pomolimo,

1795
00:47:38,840 --> 00:47:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1796
00:47:39,980 --> 00:47:40,780
[SPEAKER_00] tu i tamo,

1797
00:47:40,780 --> 00:47:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad se sjetim,

1798
00:47:41,239 --> 00:47:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] pitam ih, ono,

1799
00:47:41,960 --> 00:47:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] uz molitvu,

1800
00:47:42,579 --> 00:47:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] na čem se zahvalni za danas,

1801
00:47:44,599 --> 00:47:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] tu neku zahvalnost razvijamo,

1802
00:47:45,820 --> 00:47:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1803
00:47:46,079 --> 00:47:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer u svakom danu sigurno imaš nešto

